   version stable 0.9.9p1 0.9.9 0.9.8.1 0.9.8.0
   require mail-transport-agent slang
  category network/news
 attribute client console
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL slrn/slrn/slrn-$VERSION/slrn-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home http://slrn.sourceforge.net
      opts --with-slrnpull
      desc 'slrn is an nntp-based threaded newsreader.
slrn is an NNTP-based newsreader.
Unlike many other news readers, 
SLRN supports color terminals
and displays a thread tree.'
